#: ../../functions.md:55
msgid "Variadic functions are declared with an ellipsis as the last argument."
msgstr ""

#: ../../functions.md:57
msgid ""
"In order to call a variadic function, you must provide two Javascript "
"arguments for each additional C parameter, the first one is the expected "
"type and the second one is the value."
msgstr ""

#: ../../functions.md:66
msgid ""
"On x86 platforms, only the Cdecl convention can be used for variadic "
"functions."
